title: SET_FLY_THROUGH_WINDSCREEN_PARAMS

0x4D3118ED// SetFlyThroughWindscreenParams
BOOL SET_FLY_THROUGH_WINDSCREEN_PARAMS(float vehMinSpeed, float unkMinSpeed, float unkModifier, float minDamage);Parameters:vehMinSpeed: Vehicle minimum speed (default 35.0).unkMinSpeed: Unknown minimum speed (default 40.0).unkModifier: Unknown modifier (default 17.0).minDamage: Minimum damage (default 2000.0).Returns: A bool indicating if parameters was set successfully.Sets some in-game parameters which is used for checks is ped needs to fly through windscreen after a crash.
